message: Happy Birthday Kiara! Have a great day and a great birthday! You’ve brought a smile to so many faces in KFP, but this time we’re bringing a smile to you! Happy birthday, we love you Tenchou!
Happy Birthday tenchou! Every day is full of joy with ur stream! Hopefully we'll learn and grow together to be a better person in many more years :3! Stay healthy and happy <3

Happy Birthday Boss! Cheeers to another year for u! I hope u r having fun today~ I'm so proud of u! And I wish for ur happiness and good health 🧡 Ps. Her name's "Prinsesa", a Filipino term for princess o7
